data.description: Discover exceptional comfort and value in this Sierra Vista home, with ample room to thrive. Enter into a spacious living and dining area, perfect for gatherings, alongside a nicely appointed kitchen. The layout includes a convenient half bath downstairs, while the upstairs hosts two full baths for three comfortable bedrooms. Enjoy a spacious master suite walk-in closet and an in-suite full bath. Outside, the covered patio provides a shaded retreat, and the spacious yard isideal for BBQs and recreation. Additional amenities include linen storage, a laundry area with washer/dryer, and extra storage in the 2-car garage. HVAC replaced in 2019 and roof done in 2020! Centrally located with easy access to Ft. Huachuca and Fry Blvd shopping and dining! This one is a true gem!
